            </div>
          </div>
      
          <hr class="featurette-divider">
      
          <div class="row featurette">
            <div class="col-md-7 "style="margin-top:70px;">
              <h1 class="featurette-heading fw-normal lh-1 text-primary">The most powerful earthquake that hit the Turkey ever</span></h1>
